ole played by medical practitioners.{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s14{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\*\cs28\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up8\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f7\fs20\lang2057\i0\b0 Transcript pages 388, 602, 613}}}
{\*\cs28\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up10\rtlch\af9\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af9\langfe255\hich\f1\fs24\lang7177\loch\f1\fs24\lang7177 }  Netcare itself, and specifically in relation to this transaction, reckons its potential gains by reference to the positive impact that it will have on referrals.{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s14{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\af7\afs20\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af7\langfe255\hich\f7\fs20\lang2057\loch\f7\fs20\lang2057{\*\cs28\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up8\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f7\fs20\lang2057\i0\b0 See Netcare Internal Discussion Document, dated 4 June 2001, titled \'93Very Cross or Very Happy\'94 at page 6. See also Netcare Memorandum, dated 1 August 2001, titled \'93Medicross Acquisition \'96 Salient Features Motivation and Rationale\'94  at page 2.}}}
{\*\cs28\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up10\rtlch\af9\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af9\langfe255\hich\f1\fs24\lang7177\loch\f1\fs24\lang7177 } There is little doubt then that Netcare is not merely 
concerned to befriend the gatekeeper; it is concerned to align the interests of the gatekeeper with those of the Netcare hospital group.  We have to satisfy ourselves, firstly that the gatekeeper is an effective gatekeeper \'96 that is, can the gatekeeper det
